Package: DNAZooData
Title: DNA Zoo data package
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2023-02-09
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jacques",
           family = "Serizay",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jacquesserizay@gmail.com")
Description: 
    DNAZooData is a data package giving programmatic access to genome 
    assemblies and Hi-C contact matrices uniformly processed by the 
    [DNA Zoo Consortium](https://www.dnazoo.org/). The matrices are available 
    in the multi-resolution `.hic` format. A URL to corrected genome assemblies
    in `.fastq` format is also provided to the end-user.
